ng, D., Olson, J. S., Zhang, J., Nguyen, T., &amp; Olson, G.M. (2015) DocuViz:  Visualizing collaborative writing.  Proceedings of the 33rd Annual ACM Conference on Human Factors in Computing Systems.  1854-1874. </div>  </div>  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-view-node\">        <span class=\"field-content\"><a href=\"index.html%3Fq=content%252Fpublications-4.html\">Read more</a></span>  </div></li>\n          <li class=\"views-row views-row-8 views-row-even\">  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-field-full-citation\">        <div class=\"field-content\">Wang, D., Olson, J. S., Zhang, J., Nguyen, T., &amp; Olson, G. M. (2015) How students collaboratively write using Google Docs.  iConference Proceedings.</div>  </div>  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-view-node\">        <span class=\"field-content\"><a href=\"index.html%3Fq=content%252Fpublications-130.html\">Read more</a></span>  </div></li>\n          <li class=\"views-row views-row-9 views-row-odd\">  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-field-full-citation\">        <div class=\"field-content\">Olson, J. S. &amp; Olson. G. M. (2014) How to make distance work work.  ACM Interactions.  March-April.  29i35</div>  </div>  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-view-node\">        <span class=\"field-content\"><a href=\"index.html%3Fq=content%252Fpublications-2.html\">Read more</a></span>  </div></li>\n          <li class=\"views-row views-row-10 views-row-even views-row-last\">  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-field-full-citation\">        <div class=\"field-content\">Olson, J. S., &amp; Olson, G. M. (2014) Working Together Apart:  Collaboration Over the Internet.  Morgan Claypool Publishers.</div>  </div>  \n  <div class=\"views-field views-field-view-node\">        <span class=\"field-content\"><a href=\"index.html%3Fq=content%252Fpublications-0.html\">Read more</a></span>  </div></li>\n      </ul></div>    </div>\n  \n      <h2 class=\"element-invisible\">Pages</h2><div cla